## Overview

Implement SSHOutpost for running workers on remote VMs via SSH.

## Model

Remote VM has a full Gas Town clone. SSHOutpost:
- Connects via SSH
- Spawns tmux sessions on remote
- Uses remote git clone for code/beads
- Syncs via git push/pull

